com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Class BrowserKeyEvent.KeyModifiers

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.BrowserKeyEvent.KeyModifiers
  • Enclosing class:
    BrowserKeyEvent 

    public static final class BrowserKeyEvent.KeyModifiers
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents key modifiers that can be passed to BrowserKeyEvent instance.

    BrowserKeyEvent.KeyModifiersBuilder class should be used to construct an instance of this class.

    表示可以传递给BrowserKeyEvent实例的键修饰符。应该使用BrowserKeyEvent.KeyModifiersBuilder类构造此类的实例。
